				<li id="16561027" class="cmnt-root" data="10" data-d="1648028339000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t579605/Vyke's-Dragonbolt" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">23 Mar 2022 05:38</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16561027" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">Vyke&apos;s Dragonbolt does NOT provide the same knockback effect on attacks against you that ordinary Dragonbolt Blessing does - it&apos;s purely a weapon buff, and a lightning resistance debuff.<br/><br/>Vyke&apos;s Dragonbolt overrides Dragonbolt Blessing personal buff/debuff, but Dragonbolt Blessing does not overwrite the weapon buff, only the personal debuff. You can use the benefits of both if you use them in order Vyke -&gt; Dragonbolt.</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16561027" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16561027" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">1</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>11</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>1</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16561027"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcommen